<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="331" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="6.[853,1558,139,1965]" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">
Tubers 2, ovoid-ellipsoid
<emphasis box="[1231,1235,936,959]" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">.</emphasis>
Plant 20-50 cm
<emphasis box="[1429,1433,936,959]" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">.</emphasis>
Lowest 2 leaves 6—15(—17) x 2-6-5 cm, oblanceolate-oblong to elliptical, usually one distinctly above the other but rarely subopposite; above them 2-6 much smaller leaves passing into the bracts
<emphasis box="[1550,1554,1019,1042]" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">.</emphasis>
Spike 8-13 cm; flowers green
<emphasis box="[1212,1216,1046,1069]" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">.</emphasis>
Perianth-segments 2-4 mm
<emphasis box="[1551,1555,1046,1069]" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">.</emphasis>
Labellum 2-4 mm, narrowly oblong to oblong-elliptical, hori­ zontal
<emphasis box="[924,928,1102,1125]" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">.</emphasis>
Spur 2-5-8 mm, obtuse, as long as ovary
<emphasis box="[1434,1438,1102,1125]" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
